{"tid":1357294,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"冷靜落黎 一時之快定一世平安","createTime":"2019-07-23T16:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T17:29:45.000Z","uid":177832,"like":12,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"071074f21b3cbbab33c9dffc2c9a03b18e369f22","tid":1357294,"uid":177832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:38:41.000Z","msg":"元朗件事係好撚嬲 令人好無力 唔知仲可以做啲乜<br />\n大家好想快啲光復元朗 為當晚既事出一口氣<br />\n但其實當晚喺上環 暴力事件同樣有發生<br />\n警犬冇預警下開槍 仲要瞄頭 仲有手足喺醫院<br />\n<br />\n727當大家入到元朗 有兩個情況<br />\n一,白衫佬出黎 二,白衫佬唔出黎<br />\n如果佢地出黎 係咪要開拖？真係有刀手係咪要互片？<br />\n如果唔出黎 係咪叫光復左？係咪平安翻？<br />\n<br />\n諗返深一層 當晚如果唔係警黑合作 選擇性執法<br />\n班牛屎佬敢閪咁猖狂？ 講到底都係政府腐敗既惡果<br />\n與其入元朗同牛屎佬打 不如真真正正同翻個政權打<br />\n義士既血唔值得為鄉黑而流 不如襯仲有幾日時間 <br />\n組織出翻港島 係 如果可以打鄉黑一時間係好爽<br />\n但如果可以真真正正推翻暴政 先還到一個安全既香港<br />\n<br />\n所以 我希望大家發表下意見 727<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  be water 對準政權 轉戰港島 <br />\n        (政狗總 禮賓西環whatever)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復元朗 斬殺牛屎佬<br />\n<br />\n好民主 少數服從多數就梗 無論元朗定港島 我都會出<br />\n希望大家緊記五大訴求 可以既就加多一個？(怕太多失焦)<br />\n1. 撤回送中惡法<br />\n2. 釋放被捕示威者 <br />\n3. 取消暴動定性<br />\n4. 成立獨立委員會<br />\n5. 落實雙普選<br />\n6? 拘捕違法鄉黑 <br />\n(屌你老婆幾百萬對眼望撚住幾百人你拉6個撚化我？) <br />\n<br />\n可能會有兄弟話 咁樣手足唔平安 少左大西北參與<br />\n一, 其實班白衫佬出黎都幾個鐘前放哂風 一係撘遠啲先翻屋企 (最緊要帶衫換)<br />\n二, 大家齊上齊落 護送元朗手足返屋企 做到真正be water (一架西鐵最高聲稱可以載到2500人 當兩三車1500都嚇到班鄉黑瀨屎)<br />\n<br />\n認同請推post 好人一世平安"},{"pid":"7625b1e0cfec6a5a9253f27f5cf760c3796e9b64","tid":1357294,"uid":177832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:42:25.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"4b1720ec4bca83718209a21ef98b70fe2f40d905","tid":1357294,"uid":177832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:42:36.000Z","msg":"一"},{"pid":"efc0e2255defc3a1e0296ce40d21ba42e9595d59","tid":1357294,"uid":177832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:42:47.000Z","msg":"二"},{"pid":"dd6129e06d3a6ad802aa68aedc6221dff711eabd","tid":1357294,"uid":177832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:42:58.000Z","msg":"三"},{"pid":"93779dd21820f28a01e1eb90e893dc9f45a82884","tid":1357294,"uid":177832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:43:08.000Z","msg":"四"},{"pid":"bdaf39086b3996146e7ee22cc5a8a554267a9b8e","tid":1357294,"uid":177832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:43:18.000Z","msg":"五"},{"pid":"cb1cff87d0ade9283fe04144abaab3be9627400d","tid":1357294,"uid":177832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:43:28.000Z","msg":"六"},{"pid":"a99c64325910de53137b03a83f8c37fe39af95db","tid":1357294,"uid":177832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:43:41.000Z","msg":"七"},{"pid":"dc789cd1eee25cfbbb63ea01c142268752647fcf","tid":1357294,"uid":285433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d1fa9da020a3126d55b0252acfd77177058e767","tid":1357294,"uid":177832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:44:15.000Z","msg":"八"},{"pid":"22603775735da20b5282bc6225faa8b933dfd7fb","tid":1357294,"uid":125680,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:44:23.000Z","msg":"收皮啦！入元朗就等於斬人？<br />\n你去聽下劉細良d 分析先啦"},{"pid":"c21517aebf4baf5c930955e231a14f7098dbb30e","tid":1357294,"uid":177832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:44:28.000Z","msg":"九"},{"pid":"30931cf65eea8d1af552da669247eb22847a2a63","tid":1357294,"uid":177832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:44:57.000Z","msg":"十"},{"pid":"e0a191e54fc9a21647237205686bdcbb680e653b","tid":1357294,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:47:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35867208a72a